allegations%20are%20true%2C%20Dulat%20was%20asked%2C%20will%20India%20and%20possibly%20PM%20Modi%20be%20in%20a%20position%20similar%20to%20Saudi%20Arabia%20when%20it%20was%20widely%20believed%20that%20Crown%20Prince%20Salman%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20killing%20of%20journalist%20Jamal%20Khashoggi%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20the%20Canadian%20PM%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ENYT%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20has%20said%20he%20will%20%E2%80%9Cpressure%20India%20to%20co-operate%20with%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20killing%20of%20Mr.%20Nijjar%E2%80%9D.%20How%20do%20you%20think%20the%20Indian%20government%20will%20respond%2C%20Dulat%20was%20asked%3F%20He%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20question%20of%20co-operating.%20We%20have%20done%20nothing%20of%20this%20sort.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20official%20statement%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20has%20called%20the%20allegations%20%E2%80%9Cabsurd%20and%20motivated%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Ministry%20says%20this%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20%E2%80%9Cshift%20focus%20from%20Khalistani%20terrorists%20and%20extremists%20who%20have%20been%20provided%20shelter%20in%20Canada%20and%20continue%20to%20threaten%20India%E2%80%99s%20sovereignty%20and%20territorial%20integrity%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20also%20expelled%20a%20Canadian%20diplomat.%20Dulat%20was%20asked%20if%20the%20statement%20and%20expulsion%20are%20a%20good%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20you%20can%20see%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20deliberately%20leaving%20you%20to%20hear%20the%20interview%20to%20find%20out%20the%20answers%20to%20these%20issues.%20Watch%20the%20full%20interview%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8mzpTci1fUw%26ab_channel%3DTheWire%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695116701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fraw-modi-government-canada-karan-thapar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amarjit%20Singh%20Dulat%20repeatedly%20said