killed%5C%22%3ESepoy%E2%80%99s%20body%20discovered%20just%20a%20day%20ago%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EColonel%20Manpreet%20Singh%20was%20a%20recipient%20of%20the%20Sena%20Medal%20in%202021.%20Humayun%20Muzamil%20Bhat%20is%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Police.%20Major%20Aashish%20Dhonchak%20belonged%20to%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%2019%20Rashtriya%20Rifles.%20Sepoy%20Pradeep%20Patel%20was%20part%20of%20the%20Sikh%20Light%20Infantry%20of%20the%2019%20Rashtriya%20Rifles.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20a%20developing%20story%20and%20will%20be%20updated%20as%20details%20come%20in.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695115150000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fkokernag-encounter-ends-militant-killed-lashkar-uzair-khan%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Additional%20director%20general%20of%20police%2C%20Kashmir%2C%20Vijay%20Kumar%2C%20has%20told%20reporters%20that%20search%20operations%20will%20continue.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fkokernag-encounter-ends-militant-killed-lashkar-uzair-khan%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kiara%20wishes%20brother%20Mishaal%20on%20b'day%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695115041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103780181%2Cimgsize-169196.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkiara-advani-wishes-younger-brother-mishaal-on-his-birthday-shares-childhood-pics-see-inside%2Farticleshow%2F103780258.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103780258.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EKiara%20Advani%20took%20to%20her%20IG%20handle%20today%20to%20wish%20her%20brother%20Mishaal%20a%20very%20Happy%20Birthday.%20Sharing%20some%20pics%20and%20videos%2C%20she%20expressed%20that%20she%20misses%20her%20baby%20brother.%20Kiara%20is%20currently%20enjoying%20domestic%20bliss%20with%20husband%20Sidharth%20Malhotra.%20Recently%2C%20the%20two%20were%20snapped%20at%20the%20airport%2C%20looking%20utterly%20stylish%20in%20the%20casual%20and%20chic%20avatars%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkiara-advani-wishes-younger-brother-mishaal-on-his-birthday-shares-childhood-pics-see-inside%2Farticleshow%2F103780258.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I've%20conducted%20hundreds%20of%20interviews%20at%20Amazon%20and%20other%20tech%20companies.%20The%20hiring%20process%20may%20seem%20lengthy%2C%20but%20it's%20necessary.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221559%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Brandon%20Southern%20headshot%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F647270a33be3b50019f7220f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrandon%20Southern%20is%20a%20senior%20leader%20at%20Amazon.%20%3Cp%3EBrandon%20Southern%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrandon%20Southern%20is%20a%20senior%20leader%20at%20Amazon%20and%20former%20head%20of%20analytics%20at%20eBay%20and%20GameStop.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHe%20writes%20that%20hiring%20managers%20have%20to%20be%20cautious%20when%20hiring%20because%20their%20reputations%20are%20on%20the%20line.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESouthern%20also%20says%20that%20it's%20sometimes%20impossible%20to%20replace%20a%20bad%20hire.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20senior%20leader%20at%20Amazon%20and%20a%20people%20leader%20for%20the%20last%2012%20years%20of%20my%20career%2C%20I've%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20interview%20hundreds%20of%20candidates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20don't%20believe%20that%20the%20interview%20processes%20that%20I've%20been%20involved%20with%20have%20been%20lengthy%20or%20complex%2C%20I%20frequently%20see%20social%20media%20comments%20and%20posts%20complaining%20about%20lengthy%20interview%20processes.%20Some%20of%20these%20posts%20will%20cite%20anything%20more%20than%20two%20interviews%20or%20an%20hour%20as%20being%20excessively%20lengthy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20are%20some%20interviews%20that%20do%20feel%20excessive%2C%20many%20are%20not%2C%20and%20they%20are%20a%20normal%20part%20of%20a%20hiring%20manager's%20desire%20to%20be%20cautious%20when%20hiring%20a%20new%20employee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWork%20as%20a%20manager%20for%20a%20long%20enough%20amount%20of%20time%20and%20you're%20bound%20to%20run%20into%20a%20difficult%20employee%20situation%20that%20you%20never%20want%20to%20experience%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%2012%20years%20ago%20I%20had%20inherited%20a%20new%20employee%20that%20I%20never%20had%20the%20chance%20to%20interview.%20This%20person%20was%20an%20obvious%20bad%20hire%20from%20the%20start%2C%20showing%20up%20to%20work%20around%2010%3A30%20a.m.%20when%20most%20tenured%20employees%20were%20in%20before%209%20a.m.%20Worse%20yet%2C%20on%20his%20fifth%20day%20of%20work%20he%20showed%20up%20at%2011%20a.m.%2C%20drunk%20and%20high%20from%20partying%20the%20night%20before%2C%20and%20he%20even%20threw%20up%20in%20the%20stairwell.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20nine%20months%20to%20go%20through%20the%20proper%20HR%20processes%20and%20politics%20to%20remove%20this%20person.%20All%20the%20while%20he%20was%20causing%20issues%2C%20conflicts%2C%20and%20sapping%20the%20time%20and%20energy%20of%20everyone%20on%20the%20team.%20Dealing%20with%20situations%20like%20these%20certainly%20cause%20hiring%20managers%20to%20be%20extra%20cautious%20when%20interviewing%20and%20hiring%20candidates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20perspective%20of%20a%20hiring%20manager%2C%20the%20processes%20are%20necessary.%20Here%20are%20four%20reasons%20why%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20As%20a%20hiring%20manager%2C%20your%20reputation%20and%20career%20are%20on%20the%20line%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20any%20other%20employee%2C%20a%20manager%20is%20likely%20looking%20to%20get%20promoted%20or%20get%20a%20raise.%20But%20as%20a%20manager%2C%20this%20means%20getting%20results%20through%20the%20efforts%20of%20your%20direct%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20manager%20hires%20the%20wrong%20person%2C%20not%20only%20will%20the%20team%20not%20deliver%20the%20expected%20results%2C%20but%20the%20manager's%20decision-making%20skills%20(hiring%20the%20best)%20could%20be%20called%20into%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20risk%20for%20the%20manager%2C%20which%20causes%20them%20to%20be%20cautious%20when%20hiring%20to%20avoid%20making%20a%20bad%20hiring%20decision%20and%20being%20seeing%20as%20a%20poor%20decision-maker%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20manager's%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20The%20team%20could%20suffer%20if%20the%20person%20can't%20deliver%20what%20they're%20hired%20to%20do%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20new%20person%20is%20hired%2C%20they%20are%20hired%20to%20make%20life%20easier%20for%20the%20existing%20team%20and%20to%20deliver%20results.%20If%20the%20wrong%20person%20is%20hired%2C%20not%20only%20will%20the%20team%20deliver%20results%2C%20but%20the%20team%20may%20also%20move%20in%20the%20opposite%20direction.This%20can%20negatively%20impact%20the%20team's%20results%2C%20value%2C%20and%20brand%2C%20as%20well%20as%20individual%20team%20member's%20happiness%20and%20compensation.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20promoted%2C%20employees%20need%20to%20work%20on%20high-value%20projects%20with%20a%20larger%20scope%20and%20successfully%20deliver%20all%20projects%20on-time.%20But%20when%20the%20wrong%20person%20is%20hired%2C%20individual%20team%20members%20have%20to%20divert%20their%20focus%20from%20high-value%20projects%2C%20spending%20an%20excessive%20amount%20of%20time%20helping%20a%20team%20member%20learn%20basic%20job%20functions%20that%20were%20prerequisites%20for%20being%20hired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20this%20happens%2C%20not%20only%20do%20individual%20team%20members%20not%20deliver%20results%2C%20the%20manager%20isn't%20able%20to%20deliver%20results%2C%20which%20will%20negatively%20impact%20other%20teams%20and%20the%20manager's%20ability%20to%20get%20promoted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Bad%20hires%20are%20sometimes%20impossible%20to%20replace%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20suggest%20that%20a%20bad%20hire%20isn't%20a%20major%20issue%20because%20a%20manager%20can%20simply%20fire%20the%20poor-performing%20candidate%20and%20replace%20them.%20Unfortunately%2C%20rarely%20is%20this%20a%20simple%20process%20and%20replacing%20a%20bad%20hire%20isn't%20always%20an%20option.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20seen%20companies%20take%20almost%20a%20year%20to%20remove%20poor-performing%20employees%20from%20the%20company.%20Worse%2C%20the%20hiring%20manager%20might%20not%20be%20able%20to%20backfill%20the%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20constant%20changes%20across%20the%20business%20and%20economy%2C%20a%20hiring%20manager%20that%20hired%20a%20new%20employee%20a%20few%20months%20ago%20may%20not%20have%20approval%20to%20backfill%20the%20original%20position%20if%20they%20remove%20a%20poor-performing%20employee.%20This%20can%20cause%20a%20manager%20to%20keep%20a%20low-performing%20employee%20to%20maintain%20headcount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E4.%20Replacing%20a%20candidate%20is%20time%20consuming%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInterviewing%20candidates%20is%20a%20time-consuming%20an%20expensive%20process.%20Hiring%20managers%20don't%20want%20to%20spend%20more%20time%20than%20needed%2C%20and%20they%20certainly%20don't%20want%20to%20have%20to%20repeat%20the%20process%20in%20a%20few%20months%20due%20to%20a%20bad%20hire.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20many%20of%20the%20companies%20that%20I've%20worked%20at%2C%20we%20have%20a%20candidate%20go%20through%20an%20initial%20technical%20screening%20and%20non-technical%20screening%20before%20bringing%20the%20candidate%20in%20for%20an%20interview.%20These%20initial%20screenings%20can%20last%2030%20to%2060%20minutes%20each%2C%20but%20they%20require%20the%20interviewer%20to%20spend%20roughly%20an%20hour%20of%20time%20preparing%20to%20give%20an%20interview%20and%20another%20hour%20after%20the%20interview%20for%20post-interview%20feedback%20and%20debriefing%20meetings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20every%20one-hour%20interview%20is%20costing%20an%20interviewer%20about%20three%20hours%20before%20a%20candidate%20is%20brought%20in%20for%20the%20full%20interview%20with%20four%20to%20five%20other%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECandidates%20that%20pass%20the%20initial%20screening%20will%20be%20brought%20in%20to%20meet%20with%20four%20to%20five%20interviewers%2C%20with%20each%20interviewer%20conducting%20a%2030%20to%2060-minute%20interview.%20In%20total%2C%20a%20candidate%20might%20spend%20four%20to%20seven%20hours%20in%20interviews%2C%20but%20interviewers%20are%20spending%20three%20times%20as%20much%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20companies%20that%20I've%20hired%20for%20in%20the%20last%2012%20years%2C%20we've%20typically%20had%20to%20interview%20anywhere%20from%20three%20to%20ten%20candidates%20in%20final-round%20interviews%20to%20find%20someone%20that%20we%20wanted%20to%20make%20an%20offer%20to.%20This%20means%20that%20a%20company%20might%20have%20to%20bring%20in%2030%20candidates%20for%20an%20initial%20screening%20to%20get%20three%20candidates%20that%20make%20it%20to%20the%20final%20round%2C%20to%20hire%20one%20person.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%20the%20hiring%20team%20might%20spend%20around%20330%20hours%20in%20interviews%20to%20hire%20one%20person%20and%20that%20doesn't%20include%20the%20time%20that%20recruiters%20spend%20finding%20candidates.%20That's%20equivalent%20to%20one%20person%20working%20full-time%20for%20more%20than%20two%20months%20just%20to%20hire%20one%20person!%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaking%20a%20bad%20decision%20starts%20this%20expensive%20process%20over%20again%2C%20assuming%20that%20the%20manager%20is%20allowed%20to%20re-hire.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20candidate%2C%20meeting%20with%20five%20people%20might%20seem%20excessive%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Db04464bc88c333ccd7328d1ad7b1ac12b9657d1a3bbf3b6f5207deb7ac14b769%26postID%3D6504708ae674062ff7cfbee1%26postSlug%3Damazon-interviewer-why-tech-hiring-process-is-long-2023-9%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.linkedin.com%252Fpulse%252Fhorror-stories-interview-overkill-how-many-interviews-%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ethis%20post%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20LinkedIn%20that%20suggests%20three%20interviewers%20are%20plenty%20to%20make%20a%20decision%2C%20but%20there's%20a%20reason%20for%20needing%20a%20few%20more%20people%20in%20the%20interview%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20only%20two%20or%20three%20interviewers%2C%20one%20interviewer%20will%20be%20the%20hiring%20manager%20and%20the%20other%20interviewers%20likely%20report%20to%20the%20hiring%20manager.%20These%20interviewers%20may%20be%20overcome%20with%20authority%20bias%2C%20trying%20to%20please%20their%20manager.%20By%20introducing%20additional%20interviewers%2C%20especially%20interviewers%20who%20don't%20report%20to%20the%20hiring%20manager%2C%20biases%20can%20be%20reduced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20with%20only%20two%20to%20three%20interviewers%2C%20a%20hiring%20team%20will%20only%20hear%20a%20few%20examples%20of%20a%20candidate's%20experience%2C%20which%20could%20be%20misleading.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20team%20may%20hear%20a%20couple%20of%20great%20examples%2C%20but%20those%20might%20be%20the%20only%20examples%20that%20the%20candidate%20has.%20But%20with%20five%20interviewers%2C%20the%20team%20may%20quickly%20learn%20that%20the%20candidate%20doesn't%20have%20additional%20stories%20to%20share%2C%20or%20the%20additional%20stories%20are%20not%20strong%20examples%20of%20a%20high-caliber%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERarely%20have%20I%20seen%20a%20process%20be%20excessive%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20interview%20processes%20are%20truly%20excessive%2C%20and%20some%20companies%20even%20treat%20candidates%20as%20free%20labor%20for%20the%20company.%20I've%20been%20contacted%20by%20companies%20for%20jobs%20that%20I%20haven't%20applied%20for%2C%20and%20they%20asked%20me%20to%20write%20multiple%20strategy%20documents%20before%20scheduling%20a%20call%20with%20the%20hiring%20team.%20I've%20also%20interviewed%20at%20companies%20where%20I've%20been%20brought%20back%20in%20for%20four%20rounds%20of%20interviews%20before%20receiving%20an%20offer.%20While%20the%20number%20of%20rounds%20sounds%20excessive%2C%20I%20only%20met%20with%20a%20total%20of%20seven%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20my%20interview%20experience%20as%20a%20candidate%20over%20the%20past%2020%20years%20and%20my%20experience%20hiring%20candidates%20over%20the%20past%2012%20years%20across%20five%20companies%2C%20rarely%20have%20I%20seen%20what%20I%20would%20consider%20to%20be%20excessive%2C%20as%20a%20candidate%20or%20as%20a%20hiring%20manager.%20Many%20interview%20processes%20feel%20reasonable%2C%20given%20the%20risks%20to%20team%20members%2C%20managers%2C%20and%20the%20company.%20Even%20more%20so%20considering%20that%20candidates%20in%20tech%20positions%20may%20be%20receiving%20offers%20between%20%2470%2C000%20and%20%24500%2C000%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBrandon%20Southern%20is%20a%20senior%20leader%20at%20Amazon%20and%20former%20head%20of%20analytics%20at%20eBay%20and%20GameStop.%20He%20also%20creates%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40analyticsmentor%3F_t%3D8cgBuY7EINK%26_r%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_bla