ard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fgovt-lists-women-s-reservation-bill-for-introduction-in-lok-sabha-123091900443_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fgovt-lists-women-s-reservation-bill-for-introduction-in-lok-sabha-123091900443_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Canada%20PM%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20%26quot%3BIndia's%20Agents%26quot%3B%20Charge%2C%20US%20Says%20This%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20Canada%20Prime%20Minister%20accused%20India%20of%20being%20behind%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20the%20US%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20concerned%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20US%20was%20deeply%20concerned%20about%20the%20allegations%20disclosed%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%2C%20National%20Security%20Council%20spokesperson%20Adrienne%20Watson%20said%20in%20an%20emailed%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20critical%20that%20Canada's%20investigation%20proceed%20and%20the%20perpetrators%20be%20brought%20to%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Watson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECanadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20said%20his%20government%20had%20%26quot%3Bcredible%20allegations%26quot%3B%20linking%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar's%20killing%20with%20the%20%26quot%3Bagents%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20rejected%20the%20allegations%20as%20%26quot%3Babsurd%20and%20motivated%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20unsubstantiated%26quot%3B%20allegations%20seek%20to%20shift%20the%20focus%20from%20Khalistani%20terrorists%20and%20extremists%2C%20who%20have%20been%20provided%20%26quot%3Bshelter%20in%20Canada%20and%20continue%20to%20threaten%20India's%20sovereignty%20and%20territorial%20integrity%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20foreign%20ministry%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20also%20expelled%20a%20senior%20Canadian%20diplomat%20today%20in%20a%20reciprocal%20move%20after%20Canada%20expelled%20a%20senior%20Indian%20diplomat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20High%20Commissioner%20of%20Canada%20to%20India%20was%20summoned%20today%20and%20informed%20about%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20to%20expel%20a%20senior%20Canadian%20diplomat%20based%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Canadian%20diplomat%2C%20who%20is%20unnamed%2C%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20leave%20the%20country%20in%20five%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECanada-based%20Nijjar%20was%20designated%20a%20'terrorist'%20by%20India.%20He%20was%20shot%20dead%20by%20unknown%20attackers%20near%20a%20gurdwara%20in%20Surrey%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20row%20sent%20relations%20between%20Ottawa%20and%20New%20Delhi%2C%20already%20sour%2C%20to%20a%20dramatic%20new%20low.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20expressed%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20concerns%20about%20continuing%20anti-India%20activities%20of%20extremist%20elements%20in%20Canada%26quot%3B%20during%20a%20meeting%20with%20his%20Canadian%20counterpart%20at%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695114900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Ffneil63o_pm-modi-justin-trudeau-_625x300_11_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-canada-tension-hardeep-singh-nijjar-justin-trudeau-narendra-modi-on-canada-pm-justin-trudeaus-indias-agents-charge-us-says-this-4403280%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shortly%20after%20Canada%20Prime%20Minister%20accused%20India%20of%20being%20behind%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20the%20US%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20concerned%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20allegations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Find