3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Alex%20Cheney%2C%20a%2047-year-old%20former%20Atlassian%20employee%20from%20La%20Quinta%2C%20California%2C%20and%20the%20founder%20and%20principal%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.alittlebitalex.net%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EA%20Little%20Bit%20Alex%20LLC%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20layoff%20happened%20in%20June%202022%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flayoffs-at-softbank-backed-gifting-startup-sendoso-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESendoso%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20went%20through%20its%20first%20job%20cuts%20of%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20been%20there%20for%20nine%20months%20and%20was%20recruited%20out%20of%20my%20recruiting-lead%20position%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Frobinhood-investing-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ERobinhood%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20build%20Sendoso's%20entire%20product%20team.%20I%20was%20laid%20off%20just%20after%20launching%20the%20company's%20first%20employee-resource%20group%20as%20part%20of%20a%20newly%20created%20strategy%20for%20diversity%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20inclusion%2C%20one%20of%20my%20biggest%20passions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20signs%20before%20the%20layoff%20happened%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhiring-freeze-things-to-think-about-your-company-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehiring%20pause%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20slowdown%20in%20recruiting%2C%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bprioritization%20exercise%2C%26quot%3B%20so%20I'd%20already%20started%20putting%20out%20feelers%20into%20my%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%2017%20introductory%20calls%20in%20the%20first%20week%20I%20was%20laid%20off.%20A%20former%20coworker%20connected%20me%20with%20the%20team%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexecutive-assistant-atlassian-mike-tria-underestimate-job-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAtlassian%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20I%20heard%20it%20was%20looking%20for%20a%20product%20recruiter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20signed%20an%20offer%20with%20Atlassian%20two%20weeks%20after%20my%20Sendoso%20layoff%20and%20started%20one%20month%20later.%20I%20was%20in%20charge%20of%20hiring%20product-design%20leaders%20in%20North%20America.%20I%20loved%20the%20creative%20aspect%20of%20the%20role%20and%20working%20with%20the%20hiring%20managers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAround%20Thanksgiving%2C%20I%20started%20to%20hear%20some%20of%20the%20same%20terminology%20%E2%80%94%20hiring%20pause%2C%20prioritization%20exercise%20%E2%80%94%20and%20got%20nervous%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20time%2C%20I%20was%20also%20getting%20messages%20that%20said%20it%20was%20looking%20at%20ways%20to%20deploy%20recruiters%20into%20other%20places%20of%20the%20business%20that%20aligned%20more%20with%20the%20growth%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20helped%20curb%20some%20anxiety%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-overcome-the-stigma-of-layoffs-find-new-job-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20layoff%3C%2Fa%3E%20causes%20symptoms%20like%20those%20of%20post-traumatic%20stress%20disorder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETimelines%20for%20completing%20these%20exercises%20kept%20getting%20pushed%20back%2C%20but%20talk%20of%20deployments%20continued%2C%20so%20I%20still%20felt%20somewhat%20comforted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20just%20started%20working%20on%20process%20improvement%20%E2%80%94%20another%20one%20of%20my%20biggest%20passions%20%E2%80%94%20when%20I%20was%20laid%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20March%2C%20I%20was%20laid%20off%20from%20my%20role%20as%20a%20senior%20technical%20recruiter%20at%20Atlassian%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20received%20a%20companywide%20update%20that%20said%20there%20would%20be%20layoffs%20and%20that%20we%20would%20all%20receive%20an%20email%20within%2015%20minutes%20to%20let%20us%20know%20whether%20we%20were%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20on%20a%20plane%20coming%20home%20from%20a%20birthday%20trip%20to%20New%20York%20City.%20My%20layoff%20notice%20landed%20in%20my%20inbox%20one%20minute%20before%20the%20companywide%20announcement.%20Some%20other%20colleagues%20who%20received%20it%20at%20the%20same%20time%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20phishing%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20second%20time%20in%20a%20year%20I%20had%20been%20laid%20off.%20I%20was%20surprised%2C%20and%20the%20added%20challenge%20of%20being%20thrust%20into%20a%20huge%20hiring%20pool%20wasn't%20great%20for%20me%2C%20as%20someone%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fgeneralized-anxiety-disorder-symptoms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Egeneralized%20anxiety%20disorder%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20aftermath%20of%20the%202nd%20layoff%20was%20different%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20suddenly%20in%20a%20job%20pool%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20vying%20for%20the%20same%20jobs%20on%20LinkedIn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20recruiter%2C%20I%20had%20seen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-great-reshuffle-upward-mobility-quitting-jobs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ea%20drastic%20shift%20in%20hiring%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20being%20solidly%20a%20candidate's%20market%20to%20an%20employer's%20one%2C%20and%20it%20showed%20in%20how%20companies%20were%20recruiting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20recruiters%20get%20overlooked%2C%20with%20people%20thinking%20all%20they%20do%20is%20hire.%20Recruiters%20are%20some%20of%20the%20most%20strategic%20people%20within%20an%20organization%20%E2%80%94%20they%20have%20to%20know%20multiple%20aspects%20of%20the%20business%2C%20often%20have%20direct%20lines%20of%20communication%20with%20multiple%20members%20of%20senior%20leadership%2C%20and%20have%20to%20pivot%20on%20a%20dime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20decided%20to%20focus%20on%20family%20and%20friends%20for%20the%20first%20few%20weeks%20of%20my%202nd%20layoff%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20had%20a%20planned%20cruise%20with%20my%20best%20friend%2C%20which%20became%20a%20good%20distraction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20cruise%2C%20I%20jumped%20headfirst%20into%20a%20job%20search%20that%20was%20moderately%20derailed%20by%20my%20first%20bout%20with%20COVID-19%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20was%20likely%20good%20timing%20because%20I%20was%20getting%20virtually%20no%20responses%20from%20any%20of%20the%20applications%20and%20connection%20requests%20I%20put%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20abysmal.%20Companies%20were%20inundated%20with%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20and%20didn't%20have%20the%20power%20to%20respond%20to%20all%20the%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20saw%20lower%20salaries%20for%20roles%20requiring%20the%20same%2C%20if%20not%20more%2C%20experience%20than%20I%20had%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20made%20%24183%2C000%20at%20Atlassian.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EJob%20descriptions%20listing%20the%20same%20level%20of%20experience%20I%20had%20were%20showing%20salaries%20in%20the%20%24120%2C000%20to%20%24150%2C000%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20few%20calls%20that%20I%20did%20schedule%20led%20to%20black%20holes%20where%20I%20was%20ghosted%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fghosting-job-interview-candidate-work-careers-advice-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI've%20been%20ghosted%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20times%20than%20I%20can%20count.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20most%20frustrating%20experience%20came%20from%20one%20of%20the%20few%20interviews%20I%20did%20land%20%E2%80%94%20where%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20product%20had%20sought%20me%20out%20on%20LinkedIn%20%E2%80%94%20that%20ended%20in%20a%20rejection%20from%20the%20head%20of%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20asked%20for%20feedback%2C%20I%20was%20told%20there%20was%20concern%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bshort%20stints%26quot%3B%20in%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20and%20that%20they%20were%20looking%20for%20someone%20with%20more%20longevity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20to%20second-guess%20my%20career%20path%2C%20my%20level%20of%20skill%20%E2%80%94%20basically%20everything.%20I%20was%20heading%20down%20a%20dark%20spiral%20when%20I%20landed%20another%20interview%2C%20with%20a%20startup.%20I%20got%20through%20the%20entire%20process%20before%20I%20was%20rejected%20for%20being%20%26quot%3Btoo%20specialized.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20had%20thought%20about%20starting%20my%20own%20recruiting%20consultancy%20for%20a%20while%2C%20and%20in%20June%2C%20the%20idea%20took%20flight%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20after%20the%20Atlassian%20layoff%2C%20I%20was%20contacted%20by%20a%20former%20coworker%20from%20Robinhood%20looking%20for%20freelance%20recruiting%20help%2C%20and%20I%20took%20it%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20thereafter%2C%20my%20partner%2C%20who%20runs%20his%20own%20executive-coaching%20and%20organizational-development%20consultancy%2C%20connected%20me%20with%20one%20of%20his%20clients%20who%20needed%20help%20hiring%20for%20an%20executive-level%20human-resources%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20always%20thought%20about%20going%20off%20on%20my%20own%20but%20didn't%20think%20I%20was%20ready.%20Once%20I%20registered%20the%20LLC%2C%20suddenly%20I%20went%20from%20fighting%20for%20the%20few%20available%20recruiting%20jobs%20to%20taking%20control%20of%20my%20career%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20still%20navigating%20the%20transition%2C%20but%20it's%20been%20successful.%20I'm%20on%20course%20to%20surpass%20my%20former%20salary%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20biggest%20thing%20I've%20learned%20from%20these%202%20layoffs%20is%20not%20to%20doubt%20my%20skills%2C%20ability%2C%20or%20talent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20layoffs%20were%20a%20result%20of%20the%20economy%20and%20market%20%E2%80%94%20but%20honestly%2C%20I%20also%20think%20they%20were%20caused%20by%20companies%20scaling%20too%20quickly%20and%20overhiring%20with%20the%20assumption%20business%20would%20keep%20growing%20despite%20the%20challenges%20caused%20by%20the%20pandemic.%20It%20would've%20been%20nice%20to%20see%20organizations%20such%20as%20Atlassian%20hold%20on%20to%20their%20talent%20and%20shift%20people%20around%20to%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarting%20over%20isn't%20easy%2C%20but%20my%20network%20supported%20me.%20I%20landed%20the%20first%20official%20client%20of%20my%20business%20through%20my%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDo%20not%20ever%20burn%20a%20bridge.%20I%20had%20people%20offering%20assistance%20to%20me%20that%20I%20hadn't%20worked%20with%20in%20more%20than%20a%20decade.%20Don't%20be%20afraid%20to%20put%20yourself%20out%20there%20and%20ask%20for%20help.%20And%20even%20though%20it%20may%20seem%20impossible%2C%20taking%20control%20of%20your%20career%20path%20is%20much%20easier%20than%20you%20may%20think.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEditor's%20note%3A%20Sendoso%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%20An%20Atlassian%20spokesperson%20sent%20the%20following%20statement%20to%20Insider%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20reorganized%20our%20company%20to%20better%20reflect%20operating%20in%20a%20changing%20and%20difficult%20macroeconomic%20environment.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.atlassian.com%2Fblog%2Fannouncements%2Fatlassian-team-update-march-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20made%20tough%20calls%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20to%20prioritize%20the%20most%20critical%20work%20for%20our%20current%20and%20future%20customers.%20While%20it%20helped%20us%20streamline%20work%2C%20we%20needed%20to%20go%20further%20in%20rebalancing%20the%20skills%20we%20require%20to%20run%20faster%20at%20our%20company%20priorities.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20be%20clear%2C%20this%20decision%20was%20not%20a%20reflection%20of%20Atlassian's%20own%20financial%20performance%2C%20as%20we%20will%20be%20reinvesting%20in%20roles%20that%20better%20support%20our%20priorities.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20want%20to%20be%20clear%20these%20decisions%20were%20not%20a%20reflection%20of%20our%20teammates'%20work.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-started-business-after-getting-laid-off-twice-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695114361000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6504bcda5f9f9c0019b43d3d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-started-business-after-getting-laid-off-twice-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alex%20Cheney%20was%20laid%20off%20from%20two%20recruiting%20roles%20in%20a%20year.%20After%20getting%20ghosted%20for%20most%20of%20the%20new%20roles%20he%20applied%20to%2C%20he%20started%20a%20business.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Robin%20Madell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-started-business-after-getting-laid-off-twice-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%2BE%20Networks%20Launching%20Korean%20Fantasy%20Romance%20Series%20%E2%80%98A%20Good%20Day%20to%20Be%20a%20Dog%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695114305000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022