sts%20from%20opposition%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20speech%20in%20the%20new%20parliament%20building%2C%20Modi%20said%20that%20there%20are%20certain%20days%20which%20are%20considered%20%E2%80%9Cmilestones%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20history%20of%20every%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSuch%20milestones%20come%20in%20the%20development%20journey%20of%20every%20country%2C%20when%20it%20proudly%20says%20that%20today%20we%20have%20created%20a%20new%20history.%20In%20the%20first%20speech%20of%20the%20first%20session%20of%20the%20new%20House%2C%20I%20am%20saying%20with%20great%20confidence%20and%20pride%20that%20today%E2%80%99s%20moment%2C%20today%E2%80%99s%20day%20is%20going%20to%20be%20recorded%20in%20history%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOnly%20minutes%20prior%20to%20his%20speech%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20listed%20The%20Constitution%20(One%20Hundred%20and%20Twenty-Eighth%20Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20to%20be%20introduced%20by%20Meghwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20545px)%2085vw%2C%20545px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19142116%2FScreenshot-2023-09-19-at-2.19.56-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22545%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19142116%2FScreenshot-2023-09-19-at-2.19.56-PM.png%201058w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19142116%2FScreenshot-2023-09-19-at-2.19.56-PM-300x253.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19142116%2FScreenshot-2023-09-19-at-2.19.56-PM-1024x863.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-673715%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22459%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20first%20page%20of%20the%20Bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20comes%20a%20day%20after%20speculation%20surrounding%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20legislation%20after%20the%20Union%20cabinet%20on%20Monday%20reportedly%20cleared%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%20granting%2033%25%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20parliament%20and%20state%20legislative%20assemblies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20was%20no%20official%20statement%20from%20the%20government.%20There%20was%20also%20no%20cabinet%20briefing%20after%20the%20meeting%20late%20on%20Monday%2C%20which%20usually%20takes%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnnouncing%20the%20cabinet%E2%80%99s%20decision%20in%20his%20speech%2C%20Modi%20said%20that%20while%20there%20have%20been%20several%20attempts%20in%20the%20past%20to%20get%20this%20legislation%20passed%20and%20they%20have%20been%20unsuccessful.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20moment%20of%20pride%20for%20all%20of%20us.%20For%20several%20years%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20Bill%20has%20been%20discussed%20in%20parliament.%20This%20was%20first%20introduced%20in%201996.%20During%20Vajpayee%E2%80%99s%20era%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20Bill%20was%20presented%20several%20times%20but%20numbers%20were%20not%20enough%20to%20get%20it%20passed%20so%20that%20dream%20remained%20unfulfilled.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPerhaps%20I%20have%20been%20chosen%20by%20God%20to%20do%20this%20auspicious%20work.%20Once%20again%20our%20government%20has%20taken%20a%20step%20in%20this%20direction.%20In%20yesterday%E2%80%99s%20cabinet%20meeting%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20Bill%20was%20approved%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EModi%20urged%20all%20parliament%20members%20to%20build%20consensus%20and%20pass%20the%20Bill%20upon%20its%20introduction.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20copy%20of%20the%20legislation%20accessed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20states%20that%20one-third%20seats%20will%20be%20reserved%20in%20legislative%20assembly%20of%20the%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%20by%20amending%20Article%20239AA%2C%20one-third%20seats%20wil