ion%20(One%20Hundred%20and%20Twenty-eighth%20Amendment)%20Act%202023%20have%20been%20published%26quot%3B%20and%20will%20cease%20to%20have%20effect%2015%20years%20after%20its%20enactment%2C%20says%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEffectively%2C%20the%20new%20bill%20is%20an%20enabling%20provision%2C%20a%20step%20forward%2C%20but%20a%20separate%20bill%20and%20notification%20will%20be%20needed%20for%20the%20delimitation%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSubject%20to%20the%20provisions%20of%20articles%20239A%2C%20330A%20and%20332A%2C%20seats%20reserved%20for%20women%20in%20the%20House%20of%20the%20People%2C%20the%20Legislative%20Assembly%20of%20a%20State%20and%20the%20Legislative%20Assembly%20of%20the%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Del%20shall%20continue%20till%20such%20date%20as%20the%20Parliament%20may%20by%20law%20determine%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bill%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20of%20objects%20and%20reasons%20says%20the%20bill%20seeks%20greater%20participation%20of%20women%20as%20public%20representatives%20in%20policy%20making%20at%20the%20state%20and%20national%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20women%20only%20make%20up%2014%20per%20cent%20of%20parliament%20and%20legislatures%20in%20India%2C%20which%20is%20far%20lower%20than%20the%20world%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695112860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fljifo6ns_narendra-modi-cabinet-meet_625x300_18_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-details-of-what-womens-reservation-bill-says-4403339%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20will%20come%20into%20effect%20after%20the%20first%20delimitation%20or%20redrawing%20of%20constituencies%2C%20according%20to%20the%20details%20of%20the%20historic%20bill%20likely%20to%20be%20tabled%20today%20in%20parliament.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2