0YouTuber%2C%20while%20a%20TikTok%20user%20said%20the%20pod%20was%20unexpectedly%20comfortable.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kteo%40insider.com%20(Kai%20Xiang%20Teo)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftokyo-standing-sleeping-pods-split-youtube-tiktok-users-giraffe-nap-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Women's%20Quota%20Full%20Implementation%20By%202027%3A%20PM%20Says%20%26quot%3BAgni%20Pareeksha%20For%20MPs%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20strong%20push%20for%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%2C%20which%20has%20been%20pending%20for%20decades%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20described%20its%20passage%20as%20an%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3Bagni%20pareeksha%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%20trial%20by%20fire%2C%20for%20MPs.%20The%20PM%20said%20this%20during%20the%20Cabinet%20meeting%20on%20Monday%2C%20where%20the%20bill%20was%20cleared%2C%20senior%20government%20officials%20have%20told%20NDTV.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%2C%20which%20seeks%20to%20provide%2033%25%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20legislative%20assemblies%2C%20will%20be%20introduced%20in%20Parliament%20by%20Union%20Minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20said%20the%20bill%20is%20expected%20to%20have%20a%20provision%20for%20reserving%20one-third%20of%20the%20seats%20reserved%20for%20women%20for%20SCs%20and%20STs.%20The%20demand%20for%20a%20quota%20within%20the%20quota%20is%20what%20had%20prevented%20the%20bill%20from%20clearing%20Parliament%20despite%20being%20passed%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20earliest%20that%20the%20bill%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20implemented%2C%20the%20officials%20said%2C%20is%20in%202027%2C%20when%20the%20Census%20and%20delimitation%20exercises%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20complete.%C2%A0It%20is%20expected%20to%20have%20a%20provision%20for%20rotating%20the%20reserved%20seats%20for%20women%20after%20a%20certain%20period%2C%20as%20is%20done%20in%20the%20panchayat%20polls%2C%20where%20the%20reservation%20is%20already%20in%20effect.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20bill%20seeking%20to%20reserve%2033%25%20of%20seats%20for%20women%20was%20first%20moved%20by%20the%20Deve%20Gowda%20government%20in%201996.%20The%20UPA%20government%20then%20reintroduced%20the%20legislation%2C%20officially%20known%20as%20the%20Constitution%20(One%20Hundred%20and%20Eighth%20Amendment)%20Bill%2C%20in%202008.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%202010%2C%20but%20it%20was%20never%20introduced%20in%20the%2015th%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20and%20lapsed%20following%20its%20dissolution%20in%202014.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGovernment%20sources%20said%20the%20new%20legislation%2C%20which%20will%20be%20tabled%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20is%20different%20from%20the%20one%20that%20had%20been%20passed%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%202010%2C%20and%20so%20it%20will%20need%20to%20clear%20both%20Houses.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20constitutional%20amendment%20bill%20and%20will%20be%20called%20the%20Constitutional%20Amendment%20(One%20Hundred%20and%20Twenty-Eighth%20Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20senior%20official.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20have%20always%20supported%20the%20bill%2C%20it%20had%20been%20opposed%20by%20parties%20like%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%2C%20which%20had%20demanded%20a%20quota%20within%20the%20quota%20for%20Dalits%20and%20backward%20classes.%20In%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20special%20session%2C%20several%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%2C%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20and%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20had%20pushed%20for%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20bill%20while%20she%20was%20entering%20Parliament%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20former%20Congress%20President%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20ours%2C%20%3Cem%3Eapna%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695110340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fljifo6ns_narendra-modi-cabinet-meet_625x300_18_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-called-womens-reservation-bill-agni-pareeksha-for-mps-sources-4402985%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20tabled%20In%20Parliament%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20has%20been%20described%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bagni%20pareeksha%26quot%3B%2C%20or%20trial%20by%20fire%2C%20for%20MPs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-called-womens-reservation-bill-agni-pareeksha-for-mps-sources-4402985%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-called-womens-reservation-bill-agni-pareeksha-for-mps-sources-4402985%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-called-womens-reservation-bill-agni-pareeksha-for-mps-sources-4402985%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aaliyah%20Qureishi%20on%20dancing%20with%20SRK%20in%20Jawan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695109939000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103778154%2Cimgsize-24996.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Faaliyah-qureishi-opens-up-about-dancing-with-shah-rukh-khan-in-zinda-banda-despite-injury%2Farticleshow%2F103778000.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F10