r-Ul-Kakar%20Government%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EErica%20Robin%2C%20the%2024-year-old%20who%20won%20the%20inaugural%20Miss%20Universe%20Pakistan%20pageant%20held%20in%20Maldives%2C%20is%20being%20criticised%20in%20her%20home%20country.%20From%20religious%20leaders%20to%20caretaker%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20everyone%20has%20criticised%20the%20competition%20and%20Ms%20Robin's%20participation%2C%20putting%20a%20question%20mark%20on%20her%20participation%20in%20the%20Global%20Miss%20Universe%20Pageant%20to%20be%20held%20in%20El%20Salvador%20in%20November%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EIndependent%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ferica-robin-is-first-ever-miss-universe-pakistan-5-facts-about-her-4395765%5C%22%3EErica%20Robin%3C%2Fa%3E%20competed%20against%20Hira%20Inam%20(24)%2C%20Jessica%20Wilson%20(28)%2C%20Malika%20Alvi%20(19)%20and%20Sabrina%20Wasim%20(26)%20for%20the%20title%20and%20was%20crowned%20last%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20outrage%20in%20Pakistan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EReligious%20leaders%20in%20deeply%20conservative%20Pakistan%20said%20the%20event%20was%20an%20insult%20to%20Pakistan.%20Taqi%20Usmani%2C%20an%20Islamic%20scholar%2C%20demanded%20that%20the%20government%20take%20action%20against%20the%20organisers%20of%20the%20pageant.%20He%20also%20wants%20to%20dispel%20the%20idea%20that%20Ms%20Robin%20was%20%26quot%3Brepresenting%20Pakistan%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20politician%20Mushtaq%20Ahmed%20Khan%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWho%20are%20the%20organisers%20of%20this%20beauty%20pageant%20in%20Pakistan%3F%20Who%20is%20doing%20this%20shameful%20act%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fasia%2Fsouth-asia%2Ferica-robin-pakistan-miss-universe-2023-contestant-b2414011.html%5C%22%3EAs%20per%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EIndependent%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20caretaker%20Prime%20Minister%20Anwaar-ul-Haq%20Kakar%20has%20asked%20the%20country's%20intelligence%20agency%20to%20launch%20an%20investigation%20against%20the%20organisers%20and%20how%20they%20were%20able%20to%20hold%20the%20pageant%20without%20the%20country's%20approval%20about%20using%20its%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Kakar%20has%20called%20the%20staging%20of%20the%20Maldives%20pageant%20a%20%26quot%3Bshameful%20act%26quot%3B%20and%20an%20%26quot%3Binsult%20and%20exploitation%20of%20women%20of%20Pakistan%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Erica%20Robin%20said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20beauty%20contest%2C%20the%2024-year-old%20told%20%3Cem%3EVoice%20Of%20America%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20she%20felt%20a%20lot%20of%20responsibility%20on%20her%20shoulders%20as%20she%20believed%20it%20would%20be%20the%20first%20time%20Pakistan%20would%20have%20a%20participant%20in%20the%20global%20Miss%20Universe%20pageant.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20I%20won't%20do%20anything%20that%20would%20harm%20the%20reputation%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20winning%20the%20contest%2C%20Ms%20Robin%2C%20a%20Christian%2C%20said%20in%20an%20Instagram%20post%20that%20she%20was%20honoured.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20beautiful%20culture%20that%20the%20media%20is%20not%20talking%20about%2C%20Pakistani%20people%20are%20very%20generous%2C%20kind%20and%20hospitable.%20On%20top%20of%20that%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20invite%20everyone%20to%20visit%20my%20country%20and%20try%20the%20most%20sumptuous%20Pakistani%20cuisines%20and%20explore%20our%20enchanting%20nature%2C%20our%20snow-capped%20mountains%2C%20our%20greeneries%20and%20our%20progressive%20landscapes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20are%20the%20organisers%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20beauty%20pageant%20was%20organised%20by%20Dubai-based%20agency%20Yugen%20Group.%20It%20put%20out%20an%20advertisement%20in%20March%2C%20inviting%20applications%20from%20Pakistani%20women.%20The%20agency%20also%20owns%20the%20Miss%20Universe%20Bahrain%20and%20Miss%20Universe%20Egypt%20franchises%2C%20as%20per%20Independent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Robin%2C%20a%20professional%20model%2C%20applied%20along%20with%20hundreds%20of%20other%20professionals.%20She%20made%20it%20to%20top%2010%20contestants%20and%20then%20into%20top%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20pageant%2C%20Josh%20Yugen%2C%20founder%20of%20Yugen%20Group%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20National%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20localise%20our%20approach%20without%20changing%20the%20dynamics%20of%20the%20Miss%20Universe%20brand.%20We%20are%20still%20going%20to%20show%20women%20from%20Pakistan%20who%20are%20beautifully%20confident%20and%20who%20are%20the%20epitome%20of%20stories%20of%20dreams%20turning%20into%20realities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Erica%20Robin%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Robin%20was%20born%20on%20September%2014%2C%201999%2C%20in%20Karachi.%20She%20did%20her%20schooling%20from%20St%20Patrick's%20Girls%20High%20School%20and%20then%20went%20to%20Government%20College%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Business%20Administration%20in%20Chandigarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Robin%20started%20her%20professional%20modelling%20career%20in%20January%202020%20and%20appeared%20in%20the%20July%202020%20issue%20of%20DIVA%20Magazine%20Pakistan.%20She%20revealed%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20she%20once%20caught%20the%20attention%20of%20model%20and%20actor%20Vaneeza%20Ahmed%2C%20who%20got%20her%20into%20modelling.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695107280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F3c7dtjm_miss-universe-pakistan-erica-robin-1200_625x300_19_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ferica-robin-first-ever-miss-universe-pakistan-faces-ire-of-anwar-ul-kakar-government-4403191%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Erica%20Robin%20has%20been%20criticised%20by