ef_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2018%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20the%20last%20six%20years%2C%20I%20have%20been%20making%20eco-friendly%20Ganesha%20idols.%20This%20year%2C%20I%20thought%20of%20carving%20out%20Ganesha%20idols%20by%20imbibing%20PM%C2%A0Modi's%20'Swachta%20Abhiyan'%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ms%20Mittal%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20made%20the%20idol%20using%20soap.%20A%20total%20of%202%2C655%20kg%20of%20soap%20was%20used%20in%20the%20making%20of%20this%20idol.%20It%20took%20us%20a%20total%20of%20seven%20days%20to%20make%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Aditi%20Mittal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20Bhubaneswar-based%20miniature%20artist%2C%20L%20Eswar%20Rao%2C%20also%20crafted%20eco-friendly%20idols%20of%20lord%20Ganesha%20along%20with%20goddesses%20Saraswati%20and%20Laxmi%20on%20solid%20clay.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20ANI%2C%20L%20Eswar%20Rao%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20the%20last%2022%20years%2C%20I%20have%20been%20creating%20miniature%20art%20on%20penile%20nib%2C%20chalk%2C%20turmeric%20seed%2C%20inside%20the%20bottle%20and%20many%20more.%20I%20have%20crafted%20eco-friendly%20idols%20of%20lord%20Ganesha%20along%20with%20goddess%20Saraswati%20and%20Laxmi%20ahead%20of%20Ganesh%20Chaturthi%2C%20which%20is%20a%20famous%20festival%20of%20Odisha's%20Jatni%20village%20in%20Khurda%20district.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20also%20created%20a%20pandal%20using%20matchsticks%20and%20solid%20clay%2C%20where%20I%20installed%20idols%20of%20lord%20Ganesha%20and%20goddess%20Saraswati%20and%20Laxmi.%20It%20took%20me%20seven%20days%20to%20complete%20the%20idols%20and%20decorative%20pandal%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rao%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20height%20of%20the%20Ganesha%20idol%20is%203.5%20inches%20whereas%20the%20idols%20of%20goddesses%20Saraswati%20and%20Laxmi%20are%20about%203%20inches%20tall.%20The%20pandal%20housing%20the%20deities%20is%209%20inches%20tall%20from%20bottom%20to%20top%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rao%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20to%20spread%20the%20message%20of%20environmental%20conservation%2C%20the%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%20and%20'Big%20Green%20Ganesha'%20on%20Monday%20launched%20'Eco-Friendly%20Ganesha'%20idols%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMayor%20Shelly%20Oberoi%20flagged%20off%20the%20'Eco-Friendly%20Ganesha'%20Rath%20from%20the%20Civic%20Center%20today.%20Now%20'Eco-Friendly%20Ganesha'%20idols%20will%20be%20available%20in%20all%20areas%20of%20the%20national%20capital.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695104700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Ftc91ed48_soap-ganesha-_625x300_19_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feco-friendly-ganesh-idol-made-with-2-655-kg-soap-by-surat-artist-4402618%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20woman%20artist%20from%20Gujarat's%20Surat%20carved%20out%20an%20eco-friendly%20idol%20of%20Lord%20Ganesha%20using%20soap%20ahead%20of%20Ganesh%20Chaturthi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feco-friendly-ganesh-idol-made-with-2-655-kg-soap-by-surat-artist-4402618%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feco-friendly-ganesh-idol-made-with-2-655-kg-soap-by-surat-artist-4402618%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Feco-friendly-ganesh-idol-made-with-2-655-kg-soap-by-surat-artist-4402618%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Parliament%20Special%20Session%20LIVE%3A%20This%20Central%20Hall%20inspires%20us%2C%20says%20PM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695104419000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.busine