ath%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Rafael%20Kretschmer%2C%20a%20cytogeneticist%20who%20confirmed%20the%20hybrid%20nature%20of%20'dogxim'%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fnews%2F2023%2F09%2F18%2Fdog-fox-hybrid-dogxim-brazil-death%2F%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20only%20discovered%20that%20she%20died%20because%20I%20called%20Mantenedouro%20Sao%20Braz%20to%20request%20some%20recent%20photos%20of%20the%20hybrid%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20expert%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFlavia%20Ferrari%2C%20a%20conservationist%20who%20worked%20with%20the%20animal%2C%20said%20the%20female%20was%20healthy%20and%20there%20were%20no%20indication%20of%20any%20health%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20discovery%2C%20scientists%20said%20they%20were%20surprised%20to%20see%20'dogxim'%20rejecting%20the%20food%20given%20to%20dogs%20but%20accepting%20small%20rats.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnother%20behaviour%20of%20the%20pampas%20fox%20was%20observed%20when%20she%20climbed%20the%20bush%20that%20was%20in%20the%20environment%20where%20she%20was%20kept%2C%26quot%3B%20researcher%20Cristina%20Araujo%20Matzenbacher%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Fshelter-rescues-injured-animal-worlds-first-dog-fox-dogxim-1827353%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3ENewsweek%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIts%20discovery%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mdpi.com%2F2076-2615%2F13%2F15%2F2505%5C%22%3Epublished%20in%20the%20journal%20MDPI%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20which%20the%20experts%20said%20they%20used%20cytogenetics%20and%20other%20high-grade%20techniques%20while%20testing%20the%20DNA%20of%20the%20animal.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695103260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fc30nrgdo_dogxin-new-species-1200_625x300_18_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fworlds-first-dog-fox-hybrid-dogxim-dies-investigation-launched-4403007%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Pampas%20fox-dog%20hybrid%20had%20been%20living%20at%20Sao%20Braz%20conservation%20centre%20since%20November%202021.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fworlds-first-dog-fox-hybrid-dogxim-dies-investigation-launched-4403007%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fworlds-first-dog-fox-hybrid-dogxim-dies-investigation-launched-4403007%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fworlds-first-dog-fox-hybrid-dogxim-dies-investigation-launched-4403007%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%3A%20Canadian%20Envoy%20Avoids%20Media%20After%20Tense%20Meeting%20With%20New%20Delhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20expelled%20an%20unnamed%20Canadian%20diplomat%20today%20in%20a%20reciprocal%20move%20after%20Canada%20expelled%20a%20senior%20Indian%20diplomat%20following%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20allegation%20of%20India's%20role%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECanadian%20High%20Commissioner%20to%20India%2C%20Cameron%20MacKay%2C%20was%20summoned%20by%20New%20Delhi%20and%20he%20was%20seen%20leaving%20the%20foreign%20ministry%20offices%20after%20the%20tense%20meeting%20in%20a%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20Mr%20Mackay%20was%20seen%20grimly%20striding%20to%20his%20car%2C%20brushing%20away%20mics%20and%20avoiding%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20High%20Commissioner%20of%20Canada%20to%20India%20was%20summoned%20today%20and%20informed%20about%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20to%20expel%20a%20senior%20Canadian%20diplomat%20based%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20concerned%20diplomat%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20leave%20India%20within%20the%20next%20five%20days.%20The%20decision%20reflects%20the%20Government%20of%20India's%20growing%20concern%20at%20the%20interference%20of%20Canadian%20diplomats%20in%20our%20internal%20matters%20and%20their%20involvement%20in%20anti-India%20activities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20morning%2C%20India%20rejected%20as%20%26quot%3Babsurd%20and%20motivated%26quot%3B%20the%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister's%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20and%20reject%20the%20statement%20of%20the%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20their%20Parliament%2C%20as%20also%20the%20statement%20by%20their%20Foreign%20Minister%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAllegations%20of%20the%20Indian%20government's%20involvement%20in%20any%20act%20of%20violence%20in%20Canada%20are%20absurd%20and%20motivated.%20Similar%20allegations%20were%20made%20by%20the%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20our%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20were%20completely%20rejected%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20said%20India%20is%20a%20democratic%20polity%20with%20a%20strong%20commitment%20to%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%3Cbr%3E%20%26quot%3BSuch%20unsubstantiated%20allegations%20seek%20to%20shift%20the%20focus%20from%20Khalistani%20terrorists%20and%20extremists%2C%20who%20have%20been%20provided%20shelter%20in%20Canada%20and%20continue%20to%20threaten%20India's%20sovereignty%20and%20territorial%20integrity.%20The%20inaction%20of%20the%20Canadian%20Government%20on%20this%20matter%20has%20been%20a%20long-standing%20and%20continuing%20concern%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20foreign%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECanadian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Melanie%20Joly%20had%20on%20Monday%20said%20an%20Indian%20diplomat%20in%20Canada%20had%20been%20expelled%20over%20the%20allegations.%20%26quot%3BWe%20see%20this%20possible%20breach%20of%20sovereignty%20as%20completely%20unacceptable%2C%20and%20so%2C%20that%20is%20also%20why%20we're%20coming%20(out)%20with%20this%2