n%5C%22%3ENellayapan%20B%2C%20OSD%20to%20Nagaland%20Chief%20Minister%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201990%2C%20Nellayapan%20had%20just%20completed%20an%20MSc%20in%20physics.%20His%20older%20sister%20was%20getting%20married%2C%20for%20which%20his%20parents%2C%20who%20ran%20a%20tea%2Fsnack%20stall%2C%20had%20to%20borrow%20money%20from%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20the%20time%20before%20my%20sister%E2%80%99s%20wedding.%20People%20refused%20to%20lend%20money.%20My%20parents%20managed%20the%20required%20money%20with%20great%20difficulty.%20Till%20the%20last%20minute%2C%20the%20moneylenders%20kept%20us%20hanging.%20I%20felt%20so%20insulted.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20resolved%20to%20achieve%20something%20big%20in%20life%2C%20so%20my%20parents%20would%20never%20have%20to%20face%20such%20a%20situation%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2055-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENellayapan%E2%80%99s%20college%20senior%2C%20who%20was%20working%20in%20Nagaland%2C%20apprised%20him%20about%20the%20opportunities%20there.%20And%20the%20then%2023-year-old%20left%20for%20Nagaland%20with%20Rs%202%2C000%20in%20his%20pocket%20and%20big%20dreams%20in%20his%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20took%20me%20four%20days%20to%20reach%20Nagaland.%20My%20parents%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327829%2Flilyma-khan-head-chef-at-dear-donna-delhi-shares-struggle-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecouldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20the%20train%20ticket%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20mother%20had%20to%20pawn%20her%20last%20piece%20of%20jewellery%20%E2%80%94%20her%20nose%20ring%20%E2%80%94%20which%20got%20us%20Rs%202%2C000.%20I%20remember%20the%20bank%20manager%E2%80%99s%20expression%20when%20he%20saw%20the%20nose%20ring%2C%20knowing%20we%20had%20no%20other%20choice.%20I%20felt%20helpless%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls%20adding%20that%20the%20amount%20helped%20him%20with%20food%20and%20lodging%2