20radio%20(All%20India%20Radio%2C%20Kohima).%20In%20May%202020%2C%20they%20also%20offered%20educational%20content%20through%20a%20YouTube%20channel.%20This%20programme%20was%20led%20by%20C%20Shanavas%20%E2%80%94%20principal%20director%20of%20school%20education%20%E2%80%94%20and%20supported%20by%20Nellayapan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHeartiest%20congratulations%20to%20the%20awardees%20of%20Governor's%20Gold%20Medal%20and%20Governor's%20Commendation%20Certificate%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2F74th_IndependenceDay%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%2374th_IndependenceDay%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FqdEbUZl7OP%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FqdEbUZl7OP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Neiphiu%20Rio%20(%40Neiphiu_Rio)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNeiphiu_Rio%2Fstatus%2F1294503464827944962%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2015%2C%202020%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20hilly%20areas%20in%20the%20state%20face%20network%20issues.%20So%20we%20ironed%20out%20a%20plan%20that%20would%20reach%20every%20student%2C%20irrespective%20of%20network.%20We%20were%20also%20the%20first%20state%20to%20conduct%20online%20exams%20for%20students%20from%20Classes%205%E2%80%9312%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nellayapan%2C%20who%20was%20awarded%20the%20Governor%E2%80%99s%20commendation%20certificate%20for%20his%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWorking%20with%20IAS%20officers%20like%20Shanavas%20was%20also%20a%20big%20motivation%20for%20Nellayapan.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20had%20the%20privilege%20of%20working%20with%20many%20IAS%20officers.%20They%20are%20an%20inspiration%20for%20me%20and%20I%20wish%20to%20work%20like%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20physics%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecognising%20his%20work%20and%20efforts%20towards%20improving%20education%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Nellayapan%20was%20made%20the%20OSD%20to%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20Nagaland%20in%20April%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20road%20to%20here%20has%20not%20been%20an%20easy%20one%20for%20him%2C%20he%20shares.%20He%20has%20had%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20his%20family%20for%20more%20than%20three%20decades.%20He%20credits%20his%20wife%20for%20being%20a%20big%20reason%20for%20his%20success.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20wife%20is%20my%20rock.%20She%20supported%20me%20since%20the%20day%20we%20got%20married.%20She%20also%20helped%20my%20younger%20sister%20get%20married.%20Today%2C%20my%20wife%20is%20a%20successful%20executive%20in%20the%20private%20sector%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Nellayapan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202006%2C%20his%20wife%20and%20children%20moved%20to%20Trivandrum%20because%20of%20his%20wife%E2%80%99s%20job.%20He%20proudly%20mentions%20that%20his%20son%20is%20now%20a%20doctor%2C%20and%20his%20daughter%20is%20in%20Class%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReminiscing%20the%20past%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20concentrate%20only%20on%20work%20because%20I%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20responsibility%20when%20I%20came%20here.%20I%20had%20to%20ensure%20that%20my%20siblings%20studied%20well%20and%20my%20parents%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20borrow%20money.%20Poverty%20and%20responsibility%20guided%20me%20on%20the%20right%20path%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENellayapan%20has%20a%20message%20to%20all%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306810%2Fthis-heartwarming-story-of-determination-and-resilience-started-with-a-simple-no%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyoung%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20substitute%20for%20hard%20work.%20You%20might%20get%20the%20reward%20late%2C%20but%20keep%20at%20it.%20Hustle%20for%20a%20better%20tomorrow%20with%20focus.%20You%20will%20be%20rewarded%20for%20your%20efforts.%20Just%20work%20hard%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20let%20your%20mind%20get%20diverted.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20the%20day%2C%20many%20people%20helped%20his%20father%20with%20the%20loans.%20Even%20though%20his%20parents%20don%E2%80%99t%20require%20his%20assistance%20now%2C%20this%20government%20officer%20is%20a%20strong%20believer%20in%20%3Cem%3Ekarma%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Today%2C%20he%20supports%20six%20students%20in%20their%20education.%20%E2%80%9CGod%20has%20blessed%20me%3B%20I%20have%20to%20pass%20on%20the%20help%20to%20those%20who%20need%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oecd-ilibrary.org%2Fsites%2F61d5c87b-en%2Findex.html%3FitemId%3D%2Fcontent%2Fcomponent%2F61d5c87b-en%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EOECD%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695101867000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNellayapan-1695049811.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330237%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nellayapan%20B%2C%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20(OSD)%20to%20the%20Nagaland%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20grew%20up%20in%20crushing%20poverty%20in%20a%20one-room%20house%20in%20a%20village%20in%20Kanniyakumari.%20Exemplifying%20the%20power%20of%20education%2C%20his%20inspiring%20story%20has%20won%20the%20Internet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330237%2Fnellayapan-b-kanniyakumari-osd-to-nagaland-chief-minister-inspiring-story-went-viral-on-twitter%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22History%20Of%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20May%20Put%20INDIA%20Bloc%20Unity%20To%20Test%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20history%20of%20the%20women's%20reservation%20bill%20which%20guarantees%20a%2033%20per%20cent%20quota%20for%20women%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assemblies%2C%20reportedly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-cleared-in-key-cabinet-meeting-say-sources-4401961%5C%22%3Eapproved%20by%20the%20union%20cabinet%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20evening%2C%20highlights%20the%20fissures%20within%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20of%20opposition%20parties.%20Sources%20say%20the%20bill%20will%20be%20introduced%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20during%20the%20special%20session%20of%20the%20parliament%20that%20began%20yesterday%2C%20and%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20has%20asked%20its%20women%20MPs%20to%20be%20present%20in%20the%20house%20when%20it%20is%20taken%20up%20for%20consideration%20and%20put%20to%20a%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Congress%20and%20left%20parties%20support%20the%20bill%2C%20prominent%20constituents%20like%20Lalu%20Yadav's%20RJD%2C%20and%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20Samajwadi%20Party%20have%20always%20been%20opposed%20to%20it%20in%20its%20current%20form.%20They%20have%20fiercely%20opposed%20the%20bill%2C%20demanding%20a%20quota%20for%20women%20from%20backward%20classes%20within%20the%2033%20per%20cent%20quota.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar's%20JD(U)%2C%20which%20opposed%20the%20bill%20earlier%2C%20came%20around%20and%20supported%20it%20in%202010%2C%20threatening%20a%20split%20in%20the%20party%20with%20Mr%20Kumar%20at%20loggerheads%20with%20then%20party%20president%20Sharad%20Yadav.%20JD(U)%20had%20joined%20Congress%20and%20several%20other%20regional%20parties%20in%20demanding%20that%20the%20PM%20introduce%20it%20in%20the%20special%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20when%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-explainer-what-is-womens-reservation-bill-4402338%5C%22%3Epassed%20the%20bill%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20these%20opposition%20parties%20stalled%20it%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20SP%20and%20RJD%20even%20withdrew%20support%20from%20the%20ruling%20UPA%20government%20over%20the%20bill.%20With%20seat-sharing%20already%20turning%20out%20to%20be%20a%20big%20headache%20for%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20differences%20over%20the%20women's%20reservation%20bill%20will%20further%20test%20opposition%20unity%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress'%20parliamentary%20party%20chief%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20on%20Tuesday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsonia-gandhi-on-womens-reservation-bill-it-is-ours-4402789%5C%22%3Esaid%20the%20women's%20reservation%20bill%20%26quot%3Bis%20ours%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20ours%2C%20apna%20hai%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20when%20asked%20about%20it%20while%20entering%20the%20parliament%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIntroduced%20by%20the%20HD%20Deve%20Gowda-led%20government%2027%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20bill%20will%20be%20introduced%20in%20the%20parliament%20for%20the%20fifth%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20fifth%20occasion%20in%20last%2027%20years%20when%20a%20bill%20to%20give%20reservation%20to%20women%20in%20Parliament%20and%20State%20Legislatures%20will%20be%20brought%20before%20the%20Parliament.%20It%20was%20first%20taken%20up%20by%20Parliament%20for%20deliberation%20through%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20Constitution%20(81st%20Amendment)%20Bill%2C%201996%20in%20the%2011th%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20September%2012%2C%201996.%20It%20was%20then%20referred%20to%20the%20Joint%20Committee%20of%20the%20two%20Houses%20of%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Committee%20presented%20its%20report%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20December%209%2C%201996%2C%20but%20the%20bill%20lapsed%20with%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%2011th%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20bill%2C%20namely%2C%20Constitution%20(84th%20Amendment)%20Bill%2C%201998%20was%20then%20introduced%20in%20the%20next%20term%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20which%20also%20lapsed%20with%20dissolution%20of%20that%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20another%20Bill%2C%20Constitution%20(85th%20Amendment)%20Bill%2C%201999%2C%20prepared%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20the%20earlier%20bills%20and%20introduced%20in%20the%2013th%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20December%2023%2C%201999%20could%20not%20be%20considered%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20political%20consensus.%20The%20bill%20once%20again%20lapsed%20on%20dissolution%20of%20that%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Constitution%20(108th%20Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202008%20was%20passed%20by%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20March%209%2C%202010.%20When%20the%20upper%20house%20passed%20the%20bill%2C%20marshals%20had%20to%20escort%20out%20some%20MPs%20who%20opposed%20the%20move.%20It%20has%20been%20on%20freeze%20ever%20since%2C%20as%20it%20was%20never%20presented%20in%20the%20lower%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBills%20introduced%20or%20passed%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20do%20not%20lapse%2C%20hence%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20is%20still%20active.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20proposes%20that%20one-third%20of%20the%20seats%20reserved%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20will%20be%20reserved%20for%20women%20from%20those%20groups.%20These%20reserved%20seats%20may%20be%20allotted%20by%20rotation%20to%20different%20constituencies%20in%20the%20state%20or%20union%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20speaking%20at%20the%20discussion%20on%20'Parliamentary%20Journey%20of%2075%20years%20Starting%20from%20Samvidhan%20Sabha%20-%20Achievements%2C%20Experiences%2C%20Memories%20And%20Learnings%26quot%3B%2C%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20special%20session%20of%20the%20parliament%20yesterday%2C%20pointed%20to%20the%20skewed%20gender%20ratio%2C%20saying%20parliament%20has%20only%2014%20per%20cent%20women%2C%20and%20their%20percentage%20in%20legislative%20assemblies%20is%20just%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20present%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%2078%20women%20members%20were%20elected%20which%20account%20for%20less%20than%2015%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20strength%20of%20543.%20In%20Rajya%20Sabha%20too%2C%20women's%20representation%20is%20about%2014%20per%20cent%2C%20according%20to%20the%20data%20shared%20by%20the%20government%20with%20parliament%20last%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EState%20assemblies%2C%20too%2C%20have%20less%20than%2012%20per%20cent%20women%20members.%20Several%20of%20them%20have%20less%20than%2010%20per%20cent%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress's%20communications%20in-charge%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20yesterday%20pointed%20out%20that%20it%20has%20been%20a%20long-standing%20demand%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20to%20implement%20women's%20reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20welcome%20the%20reported%20decision%20of%20the%20Union%20Cabinet%20and%20await%20the%20details%20of%20the%20Bill.%20This%20could%20have%20very%20well%20been%20discussed%20in%20the%20all-party%20meeting%20before%20the%20Special%20Session%2C%20and%20consensus%20could%20have%20been%20built%20instead%20of%20operating%20under%20a%20veil%20of%20secrecy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695101460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Ftg2n9v3g_india-alliance-mumbai-meeting-650_625x300_01_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhistory-of-womens-reservation-bill-may-put-india-bloc-unity-to-test-4402837%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20history%20of%20the%20women's%20reservation%20bill%20which%20guarantees%20a%2033%20per%20cent%20quota%20for%20women%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assemblies%2C%20reportedly%20approved%20by%20the%20union%20cabinet%20last%20evening%2C%20highlights%20the%20fissures%20within%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhistory-of-womens-reservation-bill-may-put-india-bloc-unity-to-test-4402837%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhistory-of-womens-reservation-bill-may-put-india-bloc-unity-to-test-4402837%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhistory-of-womens-reservation-bill-may-put-india-bloc-unity-to-test-4402837%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20expels%20Canadian%20diplomat%20amid%20escalating%20row%20over%20the%20killing%20of%20Sikh%20leader%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695101460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F09%2F70x70%2Fskynews-hardeep-singh-nijjar_6290069.jpg%3F20230919065647%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhardeep-singh-nijjar-india-expels-canadian-diplomat-amid-escalating-row-over-the-killing-of-sikh-leader-12964685%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20has%20expelled%20a%20Canadian%20diplomat%20amid%20an%20escalating%20row%20over%20the%20killing%20of%20Sikh%20leader%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A135%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhardeep-singh-nijjar-india-expels-canadian-diplomat-amid-escalating-row-over-the-killing-of-sikh-leader-12964685%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhardeep-singh-nijjar-india-expels-canadian-diplomat-amid-escalating-row-over-the-killing-of-sikh-leader-12964685%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhardeep-singh-nijjar-india-expels-canadian-diplomat-amid-escalating-row-over-the-killing-of-sikh-leader-12964685%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20the%20Rishi%20Means%20to%20Hindutva%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19104342%2FF5p3YxSWsAA3PNf.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EBritish%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20India%20evoked%20myriad%20comments.%20Modi%20bhakts%20went%20gaga%20over%20Rishi%20being%20a%20practising%20Hindu%20and%20paying%20obeisance%20at%20Akshardham%20temple%2C%20while%20the%20British%20media%20and%20parliamentarians%20took%20this%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20the%20accommodative%20and%20large-hearted%20British%20system.%20In%20today%E2%80%99s%20India%2C%20it%20reminded%20me%20of%20a%20comment%20by%20Arif%20Mohammad%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20those%20days%20Arif%2C%20after%20splitting%20with%20V.P.%20Singh%20post-Mandal%2C%20had%20finally%20made%20it%20to%20the%2012th%C2%A0Lok%20Sabha%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20led%20by%20Mayawati.%20The%20BJP%20had%20just%20come%20to%20power%20on%20the%20back%20of%20its%20militant%20Hindutva%20sloganeering%20of%C2%A0%3Cem%3EMandir%20wahin%20banayenge%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0and%20a%20subtle%20yet%20not%20so%20blas%C3%A9%20anti-Muslim%20campaign.%20Nevertheless%2C%20the%20undercurrent%20was%20pretty%20evident%20even%20then.%20In%20a%20conversation%20with%20some%20journalist%20friends%2C%20Arif%20debunked%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20against%20Muslims%3A%20%E2%80%9CHow%20can%20Muslims%20be%20any%20threat%20to%20this%20government%3F%20No%20Muslim%20can%20ever%20aspire%20to%20be%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHow%20true%2C%20though%20I%20doubt%20Arif%2C%20in%20his%20new%20saffron%20avatar%2C%20would%20like%20to%20be%20reminded%20of%20that%20comment%20anymore!%20But%20his%20prognosis%20has%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20truer%20than%20probably%20even%20he%20believed%20then.%20In%20any%20case%2C%20much%20water%20has%20flown%20down%20the%20Ganges%20since%20that%20short-lived%2012th%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20which%20lasted%20barely%2013%20months%2C%20as%20we%20approach%20the%20end%20of%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20having%20reinvented%20himself%20as%20the%20presiding%C2%A0%3Cem%3Epujari%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20Maa%20Ganga.%20To%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20credit%2C%20the%20number%20of%20Muslim%20members%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20which%20rose%20to%20a%20record%2034%20in%20the%2014the%20Lok%20Sabha%C2%A0%20(2004-09)%20dwindled%20under%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20watchful%20eyes%20to%20a%20record%20low%20of%2022%20in%20the%2016th%20Lok%20Sabha.%20More%20pertinent%2C%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20choice%20of%20UP%E2%80%99s%20Varanasi%20as%20his%20electoral%20Hindutva%20battlefield%20virtually%20wiped%20out%20Muslim%20representation%20from%20UP%2C%20which%20sends%2080%20MPs%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20In%20the%202014%20general%20elections%2C%20not%20a%20single%20Muslim%20was%20elected%20from%20UP.%20Later%2C%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20the%2016th%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%2C%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20sent%20up%20Begum%20Tabassum%20Hasan%20from%20its%20pocket%20borough%20of%20Kairana%20in%20May%202018%2C%20with%20exactly%20a%20year%20left%20for%20the%20term%20of%20that%20Lok%20Sabha%20to%20end.%20And%20in%20the%2017th%C2%A0Lok%20Sabha%20a%20year%20later%2C%20the%20BJP%20recaptured%20that%20seat%20for%20their%20candidate%20Pradeep%20Kumar%20Choudhary.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20the%20late%201960s%20after%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20Jana%20Sangh%2C%20soon%20after%20Indira%20Gandhi%20became%20PM%2C%20the%20local%20general%20merchant%20would%20tell%20my%20mother%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EAur%20do%20Indira%20Gandhi%20ko%20vote%2C%20jao%20poochho%20Indira%20Gandhi%20se%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(Go%20and%20ask%20Indira%20Gandhi%20whom%20you%20voted%20for)%E2%80%9D%20He%20presumed%20correctly%20that%20my%20mother%2C%20a%20Muslim%20government%20school%20teacher%20living%20in%20Timarpur%20Babu%20colony%2C%20would%20have%20voted%20Indira%20Gandhi.%20Even%20way%20back%20in%20the%20late%201960s%2C%20the%20Sanghis%20held%20Muslims%20responsible%20for%20their%20inability%20to%20rule%20India.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20their%20ultimate%20ambition%20was%20to%20make%20the%20Muslim%20vote%20irrelevant.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETill%20the%2012th%20and%2013th%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20when%20the%20BJP%20captured%20power%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20and%20L.K.%20Advani%2C%20in%20coalition%20with%20other%20%E2%80%9Csecular%E2%80%9D%20parties%2C%20the%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20dream%20of%20jettisoning%20the%20Muslim%20vote%20did%20not%20succeed.%20There%20were%2027%20Muslim%20MPs%20in%20the%2012th%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20with%20six%20from%20UP%2C%20six%20from%20West%20Bengal%20and%20five%20from%20Bihar.%20This%20was%20considerably%20higher%20than%20in%20the%2011th%C2%A0Lok%20Sabha%2C%20which%20saw%20a%20left-secular%20United%20Front%20(UF)%20government%20with%20merely%2024%20Muslim%20members%2C%20including%20just%20four%20from%20UP%20and%20three%20from%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2013th%20Lok%20Sabha%20was%20an%20even%20bigger%20disappointment%20for%20Sangh%20supporters%20of%20the%20Vajpayee-Advani-led%20NDA.%20That%20Lok%20Sabha%20threw%20up%2028%20Muslim%20members%20with%20seven%20from%20UP.%20Some%20consolation%3A%20there%20were%20only%20two%20from%20Bihar.%20But%20then%20Karnataka%20sent%20up%20two%20Muslims%20and%20even%20Maharashtra%20sent%20one%20to%20the%2013th%C2%A0Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2014th%20Lok%20Sabha%20of%20the%20UPA%2C%20led%20by%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20a%20Catholic%20by%20birth%2C%20and%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh%20as%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20first%20Sikh%20PM%2C%20sent%20real%20shock%20waves%20among%20pseudo-nationalists.%20To%20make%20matters%20worse%2C%20Muslim%20representation%20touched%20an%20all-time%20high%20of%2034%2C%20with%20nine%20MPs%20from%20UP%20and%20six%20from%20undivided%20Bihar%2C%20including%20one%20from%20the%20new%20state%20of%20Jharkhand.%20Karnataka%20sent%20up%20one%2C%20so%20did%20Maharashtra%20and%20even%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20The%20results%20of%20the%2015th%C2%A0Lok%20Sabha%20were%20not%20so%20bad%2C%20with%2025%20Muslim%20MPs%2C%20but%20it%20was%20not%20to%20the%20satisfaction%20of%20those%20for%20whom%20Muslims%20are%20%E2%80%9Ctermites%E2%80%9D%20to%20be%20rid%20from%20Bharat%20Desh%E2%80%99%20body%20politic.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20Modi%2C%20the%20Sangh%20dream%20finally%20came%20true%2C%20with%20not%20a%20single%20Muslim%20MP%20from%20UP%20and%20none%20from%20Karnataka%20or%20Maharashtra%2C%20forget%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20That%20is%20why%20when%20Modi%20won%20in%20May%2C%202014%2C%20the%20then%20international%20president%20of%20the%20VHP%20Ashok%20Singhal%20said%20in%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20finally%20gained%20freedom%20after%201%2C000%20years%E2%80%9D.%20Modi%20has%20taken%20up%20the%20refrain%2C%20even%20in%20his%20public%20speeches%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20there%20is%20reason%20for%20the%20Hindutva%20brigade%20to%20celebrate%20Rishi%20Sunak%2C%20a%20practising%20Hindu%20who%20has%20%E2%80%9Cconquered%E2%80%9D%20Britain.%20But%20they%20turn%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20formally%20Christian%20but%20liberal%20UK%20has%20received%20with%20open%20arms%20a%20practising%20Hindu%20as%20their%20PM.%20Forget%20about%20Muslims%2C%20remember%20how%20Sushma%20Swaraj%20and%20Uma%20Bharti%20announced%20after%C2%A0the%20UPA%20won%20the%20general%20elections%20in%202004%20%2C%20that%20they%20would%20shave%20their%20heads%20and%20sleep%20like%20Kaikeyi%20on%20the%20floor%20if%20Sonia%20ever%20became%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India.%20Never%20mind%20whom%20the%20people%20had%20voted%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFaraz%20Ahmad%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695101426000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19104342%2FF5p3YxSWsAA3PNf.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwhat-the-rishi-means-to-hindutva%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Yes%2C%20there%20is%20reason%20for%20the%20Hindutva%20brigade%20to%20celebrate%20Rishi%20Sunak%2C%20a%20practising%20Hindu%20who%20has%20%E2%80%9Cconquered%E2%80%9D%20Britain.%20But%20they%20turn%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20the%20fact%20that