o%20without%20any%20option%2C%20we%20announced%20this.%20There%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20any%20impact%20on%20us%20with%20this%20decision.%20We%20are%20confident%20of%20our%20victory%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-alliance-with-bjp-in-tamil-nadu-now-says-aiadmk-annamalai-doesn-t-wish-101695033292664.html%5C%22%3Ehe%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJayakumar%20was%20referring%20to%20remarks%20made%20by%20Tamil%20Nadu%20BJP%20president%20K.%20Annamalai%2C%20who%20had%20recently%20criticised%20stalwart%20Dravidian%20leader%20C.N.%20Annadurai.%20Annamalai%20said%20that%20in%20the%201950s%2C%20Annadurai%20criticised%20the%20Hindu%20faith%20but%20was%20staunchly%20opposed%20by%20freedom%20fighter%20Pasumpon%20Muthuramalingam%20Thevar.%20Following%20the%20opposition%2C%20Annadurai%20apologised%2C%20Annamalai%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnnamalai%20has%20since%20stood%20by%20these%20claims%20and%20said%20he%20can%20provide%20%E2%80%9Cevidence%E2%80%9D%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBJP%C2%A0cadres%20want%20AIADMK%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20alliance%2C%20but%20Annamalai%20does%20not%20want%20that.%20Why%20do%20we%20have%20to%20tolerate%20the%20remarks%20against%20our%20leaders%3F%20You%20(BJP)%20need%20to%20piggy%20back%20on%20some%20party%20(for%20votes)%2C%20you%20do%20not%20have%20anything%20here.%20The%C2%A0BJP%C2%A0cannot%20set%20foot%20here.%20They%20are%20waste%20luggage.%20As%20of%20now%2C%20the%C2%A0BJP%20is%20not%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20AIADMK.%20We%20will%20decide%20everything%20during%20the%20polls%20and%20this%20is%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20stand%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fchennai%2Fbjp-not-in-alliance-with-aiadmk-will-decide-during-polls-d-jayakumar-8945334%2F%5C%22%3EJayakumar%20continued%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EState%20BJP%20vice-president%20Narayanan%20Tirupathy%20responded%20by%20saying%20that%20final%20decisions