0%99s%20charge%20was%20followed%20up%20by%20an%20official%20announcement%20from%20foreign%20minister%20Melanie%20Joly%20that%20Canada%20had%20expelled%20a%20senior%20Indian%20diplomat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20the%20past%20number%20of%20weeks%2C%20Canadian%20security%20agencies%20have%20been%20actively%20pursuing%20credible%20allegations%20of%20a%20potential%20link%20between%20agents%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20and%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%2C%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%E2%80%9D%20Trudeau%20told%20the%20House%20of%20Commons%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20raised%20the%20issue%20with%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20%E2%80%9Cno%20uncertain%20terms%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20asserted%20that%20%E2%80%9Cany%20involvement%20of%20a%20foreign%20government%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%20on%20Canadian%20soil%20is%20an%20unacceptable%20violation%20of%20our%20sovereignty%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20Canadian%20government%20has%20not%20made%20public%20any%20of%20the%20evidence%20it%20has%20for%20the%20claim%20of%20an%20Indian%20government%20hand%20in%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20killing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJoly%E2%80%99s%20office%20said%20that%20the%20expelled%20Indian%20diplomat%20is%20Pavan%20Kumar%20Rai%2C%20identified%20by%20them%20as%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Research%20and%20Analysis%20Wing%20(RAW)%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20intelligence%20agency%2C%20in%20Canada.%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocuments.doptcirculars.nic.in%2FD2%2FD02eod%2FPKRaiwsY5j.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1997%20batch%20Indian%20Police%20Service%20officer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20was%20posted%20to%20Ottawa%20as%20minister%20(eco%2C%20coordination%2C%20community%20affairs)%20in%20the%20Indian%20high%20commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20likely%20that%20India%20will%20also%20expel%20a%20Canadian%20diplomat%20in%20a%20reciprocal%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECBC%20News%20reported%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Ftrudeau-indian-government-nijjar-1.6970498%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrudeau%20had%20already%20briefed%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20leaders%20of%20some%20of%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20closest%20allies%20about%20the%20case%2C%20including%20British%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%2C%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20and%20U.S.%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJoly%20also%20stated%20that%20she%20will%20be%20raising%20the%20assassination%20issue%20with%20her%20G7%20counterparts%20at%20the%20United%20Nations%20in%20New%20York%20on%20Monday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThough%20there%20has%20been%20no%20official%20reaction%20yet%20from%20the%20Indian%20high%20commission%20in%20Ottawa%20or%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20in%20Delhi%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EGlobe%20and%20Mail%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereported%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20had%20denied%20all%20responsibility%20for%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20shooting%20and%20was%20insisting%20that%20pro-Khalistan%20activists%20in%20Canada%20had%20misled%20Canadian%20investigators.%20The%20newspaper%20said%20it%20had%20learned%20of%20this%20Indian%20response%20from%20sources%20that%C2%A0it%20was%20unable%20to%20identify%20%E2%80%9Cas%20they%20could%20face%20prosecution%20under%20the%20Security%20of%20Information%20Act%E2%80%9D%20for%20discussing%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20June%2C%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20who%20headed%20the%20pro-Khalistan%20outfits%20Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force%20and%20the%20Canadian%20arm%20of%20Sikhs%20For%20Justice%20(SFJ)%2C%20was%20shot%20dead%20at%20a%20parking%20lot%20of%20a%20gurdwara%20in%20Surrey%2C%20Canada.%20He%20was%20wanted%20for%20the%20shooting%20of%20a%20priest%20in%20Punjab%20and%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhardeep-singh-nijjar-killing-khalistan-speculation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20third%20pro-Khalistan%20activist%20to%20die%20abroad%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20month%20and%20half.%20Immediately%20after%20his%20death%2C%20his%20supporters%20had%20claimed%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20was%20behind%20the%20killing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERelations%20between%20India%20and%20Canada%20have%20been%20tense%20over%20the%20activities%20of%20pro-Khalistian%20groups%20in%20Canada%20and%20Ottawa%E2%80%99s%20perception%20that%20New%20Delhi%20was%20interfering%20in%20its%20internal%20affairs.%20The%20meeting%20between%20Trudeau%20and%20Modi%20last%20week%20at%20the%20G20%20was%20visibly%20frosty%2C%20going%20by%20the%20scowls%20on%20display%20during%20the%20photo-op%20and%20the%20divergent%20statements%20each%20side%20issued.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20in%20recent%20memory%20that%20any%20foreign%20government%2C%20barring%20Pakistan%2C%20has%20directly%20accused%20New%20Delhi%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20an%20act%20of%20violence%20on%20their%20territory%2C%20let%20alone%20a%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20allegations%20that%20Indian%20security%20forces%20and%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3Eintelligence%20agents%20have%20acted%20abroad%20in%20contravention%20of%20international%20law%20have%20been%20made%20recently%20in%20two%20high%20profile%20cases.%20The%20first%20concerned%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fdubai-princess-sheikh-latifa-pegasus-list%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecapture%20and%20rendition%20of%20Sheikha%20Latifa%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20daughter%20of%20the%20ruler%20of%20Dubai%2C%20by%20Indian%20special%20forces%20on%20the%20high%20seas%20off%20Goa%20in%20March%202018%2C%20and%20the%20second%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fchoksi-kidnap-case-antigua-polic