20bird%20is%20already%20dead%2C%20I%20then%20use%20my%20usual%20bicycle%20to%20reach%20the%20place%20and%20bury%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecalling%20a%20busy%20day%2C%20Manjit%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CLast%20year%2C%20a%20storm%20hit%20the%20city%20and%20several%20trees%20fell%20in%20the%20night.%20These%20trees%20were%20home%20to%20numerous%20parrots.%20I%20received%20a%20call%20at%206am%20to%20collect%20250%20dead%20parrots%20and%2080%20pigeons.%20All%20in%20one%20day.%20The%20two%20baskets%20attached%20to%20my%20bicycle%20were%20full%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRecently%2C%20I%20rescued%20five%20parrots%20whose%20feet%20were%20damaged.%20I%20kept%20them%20on%20treatment%20in%20my%20house%20for%20two%20months%20before%20they%20got%20better%20and%20could%20fly%20off.%20Currently%2C%20I%20have%20two%20pigeons%20and%20one%20%3Cem%3Eghuggi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(turtle%20dove)%20at%20my%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20work%2C%20Manjit%20keeps%20aside%2020%20percent%20of%20his%20salary.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20people%20have%20offered%20a%20fee%20for%20this%20work%2C%20I%20request%20them%20to%20instead%20pay%20me%20in%20kind%20and%20provide%20bird%20feed%20like%20%3Cem%3Ebajra%20%3C%2Fem%3E(pearl%20millet)%20for%20the%20injured%20birds.%20If%20I%20start%20asking%20money%20for%20it%2C%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20%3Cem%3Esewa%20%3C%2Fem%3E(service)%2C%20it%20will%20become%20a%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSometimes%20dead%20birds%20are%20stuck%20to%20the%20road%2C%20and%20people%20cover%20their%20noses%20with%20a%20cloth%2C%20but%20I%20have%20to%20pick%20them%20so%20that%20they%20are%20buried%20safely.%20Initially%2C%20my%20family%20opposed%20my%20decision%20due%20to%20this%20very%20reason%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EPar%20woh%20jeena%20kya%20jeena%20jo%20apne%20liye%20jiyein%20%3C%2Fem%3E(There%E2%80%99s%20no%20point%20in%20life%20if%20it%20is%20not%20dedicated%20to%20service%20for%20others)%3Cem%3E.%20%3C%2Fem%3EI%20consider%20these%20birds%20like%20my%20children.%20Their%20lives%20are%20equally%20important%20as%20anyone%20else%E2%80%99s.%20Their%20lives%20can%20be%20saved%20with%20just%20small%20efforts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%2C%20before%20cycling%20away%20to%20save%20another%20innocent%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20images%3A%20Manjit%20Singh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695046778000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmanjit-singh-2-1695045261.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330213%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Every%20day%2C%20Chandigarh's%20Manjit%20Singh%20sets%20out%20on%20his%20bicycle%20turned%20'Bird%20Ambulance'%20to%20treat%20injured%20and%20sick%20birds.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330213%2Fchandigarh-manjit-singh-runs-bird-ambulance-on-wheels-to-treat-injured-birds%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Experts%20issued%20warnings%20about%20state%20of%20Libya%20dams%20'for%20almost%2040%20years'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695046260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F09%2F1600x900%2Fskynews-aerial-derna-libya_6289145.jpg%3F20230918073956%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Flibya-floods-experts-warned-about-derna-dams-for-nearly-40-years-state-prosecutor-says-12964391%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Experts%20warned%20about%20the%20structural%20integrity%20of%20the%20Derna%20dams%20for%20almost%2040%20years%2C%20a%20Libyan%20state%20prosecutor%20said%2C%20as%20the%20search%20continues%20for%20bodies%20after%20last%20week's%20devastating%20floods.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.c