ission%20in%20the%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20model%20worked%20well%20for%20the%20school%2C%20Parmita%20observed%20that%20parents%20were%20taking%20money%20from%20their%20children%E2%80%99s%20earnings%20for%20personal%20expenses%2C%20including%20buying%20liquor.%20To%20address%20this%20issue%2C%20the%20school%20decided%20to%20replace%20cash%20with%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20point%2C%20for%20example%2C%2050%20points%20represent%20Rs%2050%2C%20ensuring%20that%20the%20funds%20are%20spent%20solely%20on%20the%20child%E2%80%99s%20needs.%20The%20school%20also%20partnered%20with%20local%20shops%20selling%20sweets%20and%20garments%20to%20allow%20students%20to%20use%20their%20points%20there.%20The%20school%20management%20then%20settles%20the%20bills%20on%20their%20behalf%20in%20cash.%20This%20system%20has%20safeguarded%20students%20and%20their%20hard-earned%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Ffor-Tina-1-1694608188.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Parmita%20Sarma%20and%20Mazin%20Mukhtar%2C%20the%20founders%20of%20Akshar%20School%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Ffor-Tina-1-1694608188.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Ffor-Tina-1-1694608188-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Ffor-Tina-1-1694608188-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Ffor-Tina-1-1694608188-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Ffor-Tina-1-1694608188-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329794%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E