20a%20brand%20that%20offers%20all-natural%2C%20preservative-free%20options%2C%20making%20it%20more%20convenient%20for%20people%20to%20enjoy%20their%20beloved%20side%20dish.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20what%20makes%20their%20chutneys%20unique%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20because%20these%20blends%20are%20ready%20in%20just%205%20seconds.%20The%20brand%20offers%20an%20all-natural%2C%20preservative-free%20premix%20in%20which%20you%20simply%20need%20to%20add%20water%2C%20mix%20and%20presto%20%E2%80%94%20your%20chutney%20is%20ready%20to%20consume.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBringing%20chutneys%20to%20mainstream%20markets%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFounded%20by%20two%20school%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20Prasanna%20Natarajan%20(42)%20and%20Shreyas%20Raghav%20(42)%2C%20the%20brand%20started%20its%20operations%20in%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20567px)%20100vw%2C%20567px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FScreenshot-2023-09-05-182306-1694526987.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22567%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Open%20the%20seal%2C%20add%20some%20water%2C%20mix%20and%20enjoy%20your%20favourite%20chutneys.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FScreenshot-2023-09-05-182306-1694526987.jpg%20567w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FScreenshot-2023-09-05-182306-1694526987-300x209.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FScreenshot-2023-09-05-182306-1694526987-500x348.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FScreenshot-2023-09-05-182306-1694526987-150x104.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329738%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22395%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOpen%20the%20seal%2C%20add%20some%20water%2C%20mix%20and%20enjoy%20y