y%20faces%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%2C%20Jaisimha%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAlthough%20farmers%20are%20willing%20to%20accept%20the%20technology%2C%20they%20believe%20that%20the%20more%20you%20spray%2C%20the%20higher%20yield%20you%20get.%20It%20is%20a%20little%20challenging%20to%20make%20them%20understand%20the%20importance%20of%20selective%20spraying.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20team%20has%20sprayed%20over%201%20lakh%20acres%20of%20farmland%20so%20far.%20Jaisimha%20intends%20to%20scale%20the%20technology%20to%20more%20regions%20for%20the%20same%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnowing%20that%20his%20technology%20is%20helping%20some%20of%20Indian%20agriculture%E2%80%99s%20most%20pressing%20issues%20like%20labour%20shortage%20and%20resource%20efficiency%2C%20this%20entire%20endeavour%20has%20been%20extremely%20fulfilling%20for%20Jaisimha.%20He%20is%20also%20glad%20that%20he%20is%20doing%20something%20for%20his%20countrymen%20rather%20than%20working%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20helped%20farmers%20optimise%20their%20operations%2C%20boost%20return%20on%20investment%2C%20and%20minimise%20agriculture%E2%80%99s%20environmental%20footprint%20through%20our%20revolutionary%20robotics%20solutions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20journey%20has%20only%20just%20begun%2C%20and%20we%20are%20dedicated%20to%20continuing%20our%20work%20in%20this%20sector%20and%20beyond%2C%20pushing%20the%20frontiers%20of%20what%20is%20possible%20with%20robots%20and%20automation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20Niqo%20Robotics.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694184307000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNiqo-robotics-1-1694180575.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D329484%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jaisimha%20Rao%20innovated%20AI-powered%20