0I%20came%20across%20during%20my%20practice%20is%20that%20one%20in%20four%20Indians%20die%20of%20NCDs%20(non-communicable%20diseases)%2C%20while%20the%20truth%20is%20that%20these%20deaths%20could%20have%20been%20prevented%20were%20the%20condition%20detected%20in%20time.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimple%20changes%20in%20lifestyle%2C%20she%20notes%2C%20could%20bring%20about%20a%20reversal%20of%20the%20condition.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20years%20Laxmi%20spent%20consulting%20at%20a%20hospital%20following%20her%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20nutrition%2C%20she%20came%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20a%20lack%20of%20awareness%20was%20to%20blame.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20tackle%20this%20gap%2C%20Laxmi%20started%20her%20venture%20Lami.fit%20based%20upon%20the%20solid%20idea%20that%20good%20health%20was%20within%20reach%20if%20the%20right%20approach%20was%20followed.%20As%20she%20explains%2C%20at%20the%20health%20optimisation%20platform%2C%20a%20full%20workup%20of%20the%20patient%20is%20coupled%20with%20blood%20tests%2C%20followed%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327807%2Fgautam-yadav-person-living-with-hiv-shares-myths-and-things-to-know%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproper%20scientific%20analysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20reports.%20The%20goal%20for%20both%20patient%20and%20doctor%20is%20to%20put%20the%20former%20on%20the%20right%20path.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20she%20says%2C%20will%20encourage%20people%20to%20get%20professional%20expert%20advice%20instead%20of%20reaching%20out%20for%20unsolicited%20advice%20from%20friends%20and%20family%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20health.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20works%20for%20one%20person%20may%20not%20work%20for%20another%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20cautions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20while%20Laxmi%E2%80%99s%20endeavour%20was%20proving%20successful%2C%20she%20points%20to%20certain%20gaps%20that%20she%20struggled%20with%20as%20someone%20who%20was%20a%20novice%20to%20the%20business%20world.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20add%20to%20this%20I%20was%20a%20woman%20entrepreneur%20entering%20a%20new%20field.%20There%20were%20many%20areas%20that%20I%20needed%20assistance%20with%20%E2%80%94%20pitching%20presentations%2C%20interacting%20with%20other%20professionals%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329202%2Fgwalior-professor-nidhi-katare-becomes-successful-mushroom-farmer-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emarketing%20the%20brand%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20product%2C%20etc.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FI-WIN_TBI_02-1-1-1694182758.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22I-Venture%20%40%20ISB%20Women%20of%20Innovation%20(I-WIN)%20Program%20helps%20women%20entrepreneurs%20scale%20their%20startups%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FI-WIN_TBI_02-1-1-1694182758.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FI-WIN_TBI_02-1-1-1694182758-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FI-WIN_TBI_02-1-1-1694182758-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FI-WIN_TBI_02-1-1-1694182758-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FI-WIN_TBI_02-1-1-1694182758-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329507%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%20I-Venture%20%40%20ISB%20Women%20of%20Innovation%20(I-WIN)%20Program%20helps%20women%20entrepreneurs%20scale%20their%20startups%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20ISB%3C%2Ffigcaption%3