0sat%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323084%2Fmumbai-mother-son-duo-start-aazol-maharastrian-traditional-snacks-help-rural-women%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewomen%20entrepreneurs%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20understand%20the%20challenges%20they%20encountered%20in%20business%2C%20they%20began%20to%20understand%20these%20were%20common.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20of%20them%20shared%20that%20while%20policies%20are%20in%20place%20to%20help%20women%20entrepreneurs%2C%20there%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20awareness.%20They%20were%20thus%20in%20need%20of%20a%20platform%20or%20community%20that%20would%20support%20them%20through%20the%20entire%20process.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20how%20the%20I-WIN%20program%20came%20into%20existence.%20We%20simply%20wanted%20to%20handhold%20these%20women%20entrepreneurs%20in%20their%20journey%20and%20leverage%20our%20network%20for%20the%20purpose.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EArming%20women%20entrepreneurs%20with%20vital%20resources%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FI-WIN_TBI_01-1-1694182836.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20first%20cohort%20of%20the%20I-Venture%20%40%20ISB%20Women%20of%20Innovation%20(I-WIN)%20Program%20sees%20startups%20from%20numerous%20domains%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FI-WIN_TBI_01-1-1694182836.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FI-WIN_TBI_01-1-1694182836-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FI-WIN_TBI_01-1-1694182836-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.theb